ny that it's annoying sometimes, but I felt like I should work harder because you were pushing me.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"remakestory-24-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"I wanted to try hard, but I was doing it on my own. While I was so focused on that, I wasn't paying any attention to you guys.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"remakestory-24-089","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"(We'll be fine after all those rehearsals we did...! We're gonna give it everything we've got, all the way through to the end...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-063","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"(I can't just pay attention to my own playing... I have to listen to everyone else so we can bring it all together...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-064","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"(I can tell by listening to each of our sounds... We've done a lot of practice, and we've gotten better...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-065","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"(Kasumi's doing really well... I'll back her up with my drumming...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-066","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"(I'm getting the sparkling and heart-pounding feeling from you guys...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-068","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":215}],"windowDisplayName":"Owner","body":"Doesn't look like I have to ask those four. Let's hear it from you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":215,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":215,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-077","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"... I gave it everything I had!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-078","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":215}],"windowDisplayName":"Owner","body":"Great show... You're in.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":215,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":215,"voiceId":"remakestory-26-080","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Surprised at how big the venue is?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-03-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"window